BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
Call the generating function [`A\text{.}`] Compute [`A - xA = 4 + x + 2x^2 + 3x^3 + 4x^4 + \cdots\text{.}`] Thus [`A - xA = 4 + \dfrac{x}{(1-x)^2}\text{.}`] Solving for [`A`] gives [`\d\frac{4}{1-x} + \frac{x}{(1-x)^3}\text{.}`]

